{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to this wavefront-shaping based wave control for coherently enhanced absorption, we also consider the possibility of controlling both the input wavefront and the metasurface configuration to maximize the absorbed energy.",
    "To that end, we use the physical model to select a metasurface configuration out of the 10 5 configurations from the calibration data set that we expect to yield maximal absorption of energy.",
    "Even though these configurations were part of the calibration data, because the latter was phaseless in the case of Fig. 3f and lacked one relevant transmission coefficient in the case of Fig.",
    "S2b, our ability to identify a metasurface configuration that maximizes the coherently enhanced absorbed energy is remarkable.",
    "Details for the dictionary-search-based inverse-design algorithm are similar to those described for coherent focusing above."
  ]
}